{"tid":660482,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我呀嫲隻耳變到好差","createTime":"2018-05-10T17:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T17:48:07.000Z","uid":6636,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"36ae3536b2c3b0ec0fed2d902d7349cb7950b1d8","tid":660482,"uid":6636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T17:00:00.000Z","msg":"最近同佢講野一定要好大聽先聽到，我覺得佢好多時都係估我講啲咩，未睇醫生前仲好過而家睇咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 突然間見到佢咁真係覺得佢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明前排仲有傾有講有笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  究竟點先幫到佢，醫生話佢未必適合配助聽器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日同唔到人傾計好辛苦架一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64b996e03da000df689cf1d9bbdcc5790650e70","tid":660482,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T17:06:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f01959eed6698e2245b802a68aca61f22da580c","tid":660482,"uid":144325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T17:07:46.000Z","msg":"同佢傾計個陣大聲啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65bea0446d9641916f4c1f7eb2caace8db93e5e1","tid":660482,"uid":6636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f01959eed6698e2245b802a68aca61f22da580c","tid":660482,"uid":144325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T17:07:46.000Z","msg":"同佢傾計個陣大聲啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T17:12:09.000Z","msg":"我嗌出嚟佢都唔係好聽到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"