邊慢慢同佢講野 多d 身體動作 等佢快d 理解到  <br />\n帶耳機會放大哂身邊所有聲 而且掛係耳仔唔舒服 好多老人家唔鍾意戴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T17:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c644b5e16ac61679e6b6e095d1e7c464f63651","tid":660482,"uid":131741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T17:48:07.000Z","msg":"我嫲嫲都係<br />\n無幾耐之前發現佢聽覺開始差，成日個電視開到好大聲都聽唔到<br />\n同佢去配咗掛耳嗰啲助聽器，雖然佢唔太鍾意但無奈都要用<br />\n好快就連喺佢耳邊大聲講都淨係聽到少少，再去check就話佢真係又弱咗<br />\n咁唯有係講野嗰陣加多啲肢體動作<br />\n多啲拖下佢手，攬下佢，等佢喺變得寧靜嘅世界可以感受到我地仲關心緊佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢前排走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都仲好唔捨得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 記得要珍惜眼前嘅佢啊！"}]}